text.section:
A foreign entity shall register its real name, or its real name with any addition required by KRS 14A.3-010, by delivering to the Secretary of State for filing an application setting forth:
Its real name, or its real name with any addition required by KRS 14A.3-010;
The state or country of its organization;
Its form of organization;
Its principal office address; and
A brief description of the nature of the business in which it is engaged.
